# Most SVGs in this repo are generated by profile.py or approach.py,
# not authored by hand (approach.svg is the one exception - it's the hand-edited source
# approach.py derives its dark/light siblings from). Marking them all
# generated keeps each forge's language bar on Python rather than SVG and collapses the
# noisy per-build SVG diffs in reviews.
*.svg linguist-generated=true
